text: Kristabel Doebel-Hickok (born April 28, 1989) is an American professional racing cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Women's Continental Team . ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:American female cyclists Category:People from Marina del Rey, California
